title: Sonos BOOST
description:
Sonos BOOST is an accessory that establishes a powerful wireless network exclusively for your Sonos speakers. It increases wireless range and eliminates interference, so you can stream, surf, and game all you want without missing a beat. BOOST also connects SUB and rear speakers to your PLAYBAR for an immersive surround-sound home theater experience.

Sonos Your Home 
All your music in every room in amazing HiFi sound. Wirelessly.

Abt is a proud authorized retailer of Sonos Home Audio products. Shop for the Sonos BOOST and the full line of Sonos Home Audio products at Abt!
